Nordic Electricity Market Intelligence & Price Forecasting Platform

An AI-driven electricity market analytics and forecasting platform built using real Finland day-ahead electricity pricing data from the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform. This project focuses on electricity market trend analysis, electricity price forecasting, volatility detection, and market intelligence using machine learning and time-series analytics.

Project Overview

This project analyzes real-world Nordic electricity market behavior using Finland’s electricity pricing data from the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform. The platform performs:

Electricity price trend analysis
Market volatility detection
Time-series analytics
Machine learning-based forecasting
Market behavior visualization

The system demonstrates how AI and data analytics can support electricity market forecasting and energy intelligence systems.

Key Features
Real Finland electricity market data analysis
Day-ahead electricity price forecasting
Time-series analytics and visualization
Market volatility detection
Hourly electricity price analysis
Monthly and seasonal trend analysis
Feature engineering for forecasting
Machine learning model training and evaluation
Interactive Streamlit dashboard
Energy market insights generation
