Dataset Information

The dataset was collected from the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform and contains real Finland electricity market pricing data.

Dataset Includes:
Timestamp
Day-ahead electricity prices (EUR/MWh)
Historical electricity market data
High-frequency pricing intervals
Project Workflow
1. Data Collection

Real Finland electricity market pricing data was downloaded from the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform.

2. Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
Removed unnecessary columns
Converted timestamps
Processed electricity pricing data
Handled missing values
3. Feature Engineering

Generated time-based features:

Hour
Day
Month
Weekday
Year
4. Exploratory Data Analysis

Performed:

Electricity price trend analysis
Hourly pricing pattern analysis
Monthly market behavior analysis
Market volatility analysis
5. Machine Learning Forecasting

Trained a Random Forest Regression model to forecast electricity prices using time-based features.

6. Model Evaluation

Evaluated forecasting performance using:

MAE
MSE
RMSE
R² Score
7. Volatility Detection

Detected abnormal electricity price spikes and unstable market periods.

Machine Learning Model
Model Used
Random Forest Regressor
Input Features
Hour
